theme-app-description =
    FreeSynergy Themes manages the visual appearance of the entire FreeSynergy platform.

    Install themes from the Store, switch between them, and customize individual
    properties: accent colors, background colors, typography, cursor style, and
    window chrome. All FreeSynergy apps respond to theme changes in real time
    via CSS custom properties — no restart required.

    The three built-in themes (Midnight Blue, Nordic Dark, Cloud White) can be
    used as starting points for custom themes.

theme-app-features =
    - Install themes from the Store with one click
    - Switch themes platform-wide in real time
    - Per-user theme preferences (overrides node-wide default)
    - Accent color picker with contrast validation
    - Typography selection (font family, size, line height)
    - Cursor style and size settings
    - Export custom theme as a Store-compatible theme package
